name: Hinata Hyuga Character LoRA
description:
Hinata Hyuga Character LoRA

If you enjoy my models and want to support me you could buy me a coffee!

This LoRA mimics the character Hinata Hyuga from Naruto.

The example images were created with NeverEndingDream on varying weight but feel free to experiment on your own. I tried briefly to mix it with a couple of different embeddings and it gave back decent results but you might find a better way to mix them (changing different weights etc.).

I did mess up a little bit in the creation of the LoRA so it sometimes gives you some text in the corner in a watermark-type style. Also you could need to add "collar, choker, konohagakure symbol" to the negative prompts if you don't want the headband.

To change the weight just change the '1' in this prompt: <lora:hinata-Hyuga-LoRA:1>.

I'd love to see the art you guys make with it so feel free to add them in comments.

How to use LoRA's in auto1111:

  • Update webui (use git pull like here or redownload it)

  • Copy the file to stable-diffusion-webui/models/lora

  • Select your LoRA like in this video

  • Make sure to change the weight (by default it's :1 which is usually too high)
